<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday Riddhisha ✈️🎂</title>

<style>
    *{
        margin:0;
        padding:0;
        box-sizing:border-box;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    body{
        height:100vh;
        display:flex;
        justify-content:center;
        align-items:center;
        background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);
        overflow:hidden;
    }

    .stars{
        position:absolute;
        width:100%;
        height:100%;
        background:url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png');
        opacity:0.4;
        animation:move 30s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes move{
        from{transform:translateY(0);}
        to{transform:translateY(-100px);}
    }

    .card{
        position:relative;
        z-index:1;
        width:90%;
        max-width:700px;
        background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
        border-radius:25px;
        padding:40px;
        text-align:center;
        color:white;
        box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }

    h1{
        font-size:3rem;
        color:#ffd700;
        margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    h2{
        font-size:1.5rem;
        margin-bottom:25px;
    }

    p{
        font-size:1.15rem;
        line-height:1.8;
        margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    .quote{
        font-style:italic;
        color:#87cefa;
        font-size:1.2rem;
    }

    .plane{
        font-size:70px;
        animation:fly 5s ease-in-out infinite;
        display:inline-block;
    }

    @keyframes fly{
        0%{transform:translateX(-20px) rotate(-10deg);}
        50%{transform:translateX(20px) rotate(10deg);}
        100%{transform:translateX(-20px) rotate(-10deg);}
    }

    button{
        margin-top:20px;
        padding:12px 25px;
        border:none;
        border-radius:30px;
        background:#ffd700;
        color:#000;
        font-size:18px;
        cursor:pointer;
        font-weight:bold;
    }

    button:hover{
        transform:scale(1.05);
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="stars"></div>

<div class="card">

    <div class="plane">✈️</div>

    <h1>Happy Birthday</h1>
    <h2>Riddhisha ❤️</h2>

    <p>
        Today is not just your birthday, it's a celebration of your dreams,
        your courage, and the incredible journey you're on.
    </p>

    <p>
        As an <b>Aviation Trainee</b>, you are learning not only to fly aircraft,
        but also to fly above doubts and challenges.
    </p>

    <p class="quote">
        "The sky is not your limit, Riddhisha — it's just the beginning."
    </p>

    <p>
        Keep dreaming big, keep working hard, and never stop believing in yourself.
        One day you'll look back and realize that every small step brought you
        closer to the clouds you always wanted to touch.
    </p>

    <p>
        May this year bring you happiness, success, endless adventures,
        and wings strong enough to carry all your dreams.
    </p>

    <button onclick="wish()">Click for a Surprise 🎁</button>

</div>

<script>
function wish(){
    alert("🎂 Happy Birthday Riddhisha! ✈️\n\nMay your dreams soar higher than the skies and your future shine brighter than the stars.\nKeep flying, Dreamer! ❤️");
}
</script>

</body>
</html>